The site outlined the four incidents that Mourinho had highlighted in minutes 30, 33, 43 and 69: an unpunished challenge from Burnley's Ashley Barnes on Branislav Ivanovic; being denied two 'clear' penalties and a shocking Barnes' challenge on Nemanja Matic - again unpunished.

